    text: "Designers cost $5K/month. Competitor research means scrolling their site for 20 minutes. Your ads go stale and your messaging sounds like everyone else. There's a better way.",
    link: "/projects"
  },
  {
    icon: "M9 3H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 012 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 002-2V9M9 21H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9m0 0h18",
