---

<section class="problem bg-surface" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2>Sound Familiar?</h2>
      <p>These are the problems we solve. Every day. For businesses like yours.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pain-grid" data-animate-stagger>
      {painPoints.map((pain) => (
        <a href={pain.link} class="pain-card card">
          <span class="pain-icon icon-circle icon-circle-blue">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d={pain.icon}></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <h3>{pain.title}</h3>
          <p>{pain.text}</p>
          <span class="pain-link">See the fix &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="bottom-stat" data-animate="fade-up">
      <p>You're great at what you do. But between client work and operations, the busywork keeps piling up. <strong>It doesn't have to.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pain-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Stays at 2 columns on large screens (2x2 layout for 4 categories) */

  .pain-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }

  .pain-card:hover {
    color: inherit;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .pain-card:hover .pain-link {
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .pain-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
  }

  .pain-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .pain-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .pain-link {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .bottom-stat {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bottom-stat p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .bottom-stat strong {
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bottom-stat {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
